name: Bahar Tehranipoor
about: Hi! My name is Bahar and I'm a sophomore majoring in computer science and minoring in business. On-campus I'm the assistant musical director of my acapella group The Touchtones and a web dev on The Wardrobe. Outside of all that, you can find me watching documentaries (usually about pyramid schemes), listening to new music, or reading a book and updating my Goodreads.
